# XFlickr architecture

Read [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) and skill [`ai/skills/form-request-service-repository/SKILL.md`](../../ai/skills/form-request-service-repository/SKILL.md).

Flow: `Controller → FormRequest → Service → Repository → Model`

- Crawl logic: `jooservices/xflickr-crawler` package only
- Spider mode: opt-in (`spider.enabled` runtime config); see `SpiderPlannerService` and `docs/02-user-guide/spider-mode.md`
- Jobs delegate to Services

Module map: [`ai/skills/class-purpose-and-module-map/SKILL.md`](../../ai/skills/class-purpose-and-module-map/SKILL.md)
